\n## Cần lên kế hoạch chi tiết:\n1. Phân tích các entities cần phân quyền\n2. Xác định owner-field mapping (ai sở hữu data nào)\n3. Thiết kế middleware/helper cho data isolation\n4. Lộ trình implementation từng bước\n5. Frontend considerations\n\nHãy cụ thể hóa yêu cầu này thành SPEC chi tiết để triển khai.","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"prompt-optimizer","mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1187,"output":766,"cacheRead":79600,"cacheWrite":1365,"totalTokens":82918,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776742362859,"responseId":"063622dc860a75f4e83875798d1bdcf0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"027bbfd5","parentId":"fd5cc9c2","timestamp":"2026-04-21T03:32:56.103Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_skoa3jykrqvg_1","toolName":"sessions_spawn","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"accepted\",\n  \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:prompt-optimizer:subagent:49621252-eb7d-4bad-9082-6a98331cfd33\",\n  \"runId\": \"15d746d5-f2e0-4d6a-9a00-592583c91ab0\",\n  \"mode\": \"run\",\n  \"note\": \"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Wait for completion events to arrive as user messages, track expected child session keys, and only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER your final answer, reply ONLY with NO_REPLY.\",\n  \"modelApplied\": true\n}"}],"details":{"status":"accepted","childSessionKey":"agent:prompt-optimizer:subagent:49621252-eb7d-4bad-9082-6a98331cfd33","runId":"15d746d5-f2e0-4d6a-9a00-592583c91ab0","mode":"run","note":"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Wait for completion events to arrive as user messages, track expected child session keys, and only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER your final answer, reply ONLY with NO_REPLY.","modelApplied":true},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776742376096}}
{"type":"message","id":"4e6f52ad","parentId":"027bbfd5","timestamp":"2026-04-21T03:33:01.106Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the agent is spawned. Let me wait for the completion. In the meantime, let me also check a few more controllers that need checking.","thinkingSignature":"b73695e89ef937e1a1ec5396607e7c7bd3e868bf8aba0586d53d9f2ab29d4ded"},{"type":"text","text":"Đã spawn prompt-optimizer agent để cụ thể hóa yêu cầu. Trong khi chờ, mình kiểm tra thêm các controller còn lại:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7i4d50qopxhg_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/exam_batch.controller.ts"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7i4d50qopxhg_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/stadium.controller.ts"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":249,"output":169,"cacheRead":80934,"cacheWrite":1922,"totalTokens":83274,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776742376106,"responseId":"063622e904fdcef77ea2d0d7cc78b570"}}
{"type":"message","id":"48342025","parentId":"4e6f52ad","timestamp":"2026-04-21T03:33:01.138Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7i4d50qopxhg_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { Request, Response } from 'express';\nimport { ExamBatchService } from '@/application/services/exam_batch.service';\nimport { ExamBatchRepository } from '@/infrastructure/database/repositories/exam_batch.repository';\nimport { catchAsync } from '@/interface/middlewares/catchAsync.middleware';\nimport * as fs from 'fs';\n\nconst examBatchRepository = new ExamBatchRepository();\nconst examBatchService = new ExamBatchService(examBatchRepository);\n\nexport const createBatch = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n  const batch = await examBatchService.createBatch(req.body);\n  res.statusSuccess(batch, 'Exam batch created successfully');\n});\n\nexport const getAllBatches = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n  const batches = await examBatchService.getAllBatches(req.pagination);\n  res.statusSuccess(batches, 'Exam batches retrieved successfully');\n});\n\nexport const getBatchById = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n  const batch = await examBatchService.getBatchById((typeof req.params.id === 'string' ? req.params.id : req.params.id[0]));\n  if (!batch) {\n    return res.statusError('Exam batch not found', 404);\n  }\n  res.statusSuccess(batch, 'Exam batch retrieved successfully');\n});\n\nexport const updateBatch = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n  const batch = await examBatchService.updateBatch((typeof req.params.id === 'string' ? req.params.id : req.params.id[0]), req.body);\n  if (!batch) {\n    return res.statusError('Exam batch not found', 404);\n  }\n  res.statusSuccess(batch, 'Exam batch updated successfully');\n});\n\nexport const deleteBatch = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n  const idStr = typeof req.params.id === 'string' ? req.params.id : req.params.id[0];\n  await examBatchService.deleteBatch(idStr);\n  res.statusSuccess(null, 'Exam batch deleted successfully');\n});\n\nexport const exportBatches = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n  await examBatchService.exportBatchesToExcel(res, req.query);\n});\n\nexport const getStats = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n  const stats = await examBatchService.getStats();\n  res.statusSuccess(stats, 'Exam batch statistics retrieved successfully');\n});\n\nexport const getBatchStats = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n  const idStr = typeof req.params.id === 'string' ? req.params.id : req.params.id[0];\n  const stats = await examBatchService.getBatchStats(idStr);\n  if (!stats) return res.statusError('Batch not found', 404);\n  res.statusSuccess(stats, 'Batch stats retrieved successfully');\n});\n\nexport const importResults = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n  if (!req.file) {\n    return res.statusError('No file uploaded', 400);\n  }\n\n  const batchId = typeof req.params.id === 'string' ? req.params.id : req.params.id[0];\n  const results = await examBatchService.importResults(batchId, req.file.path);\n  \n  // Clean up uploaded file\n  if (fs.existsSync(req.file.path)) {\n    fs.unlinkSync(req.file.path);\n  }\n\n  res.statusSuccess(results, 'Exam results imported successfully');\n});\n\nexport const getImportTemplate = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n  await examBatchService.getTemplate(res);\n});\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776742381131}}
{"type":"message","id":"39b71cb3","parentId":"48342025","timestamp":"2026-04-21T03:33:01.145Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7i4d50qopxhg_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { Request, Response } from 'express';\nimport { StadiumService } from '@/application/services/stadium.service';\nimport { catchAsync } from '@/interface/middlewares/catchAsync.middleware';\n\nexport class StadiumController {\n  private stadiumService: StadiumService;\n\n  constructor() {\n    this.stadiumService = new StadiumService();\n    this.getAll = this.getAll.bind(this);\n    this.getById = this.getById.bind(this);\n    this.create = this.create.bind(this);\n    this.update = this.update.bind(this);\n    this.delete = this.delete.bind(this);\n  }\n\n  getAll = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n    const { page, limit, city, search, region_id } = req.query;\n    const result = await this.stadiumService.getAllStadiums(\n      { \n        city: city as string, \n        region_id: region_id as string,\n        search: search as string \n      },\n      { page: Number(page) || 1, limit: Number(limit) || 10 }\n    );\n    (res as any).statusSuccess({\n      items: result.docs,\n      pagination: {\n        total: result.total,\n        page: result.page,\n        limit: result.limit,\n        totalPages: result.totalPages\n      }\n    }, 'Stadiums retrieved successfully');\n  });\n\n  getById = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n    const stadium = await this.stadiumService.getStadiumById(req.params.id as string);\n    if (!stadium) {\n      return res.status(404).json({ success: false, message: 'Stadium not found' });\n    }\n    res.json({ success: true, data: stadium });\n  });\n\n  create = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n    const stadium = await this.stadiumService.createStadium(req.body);\n    (res as any).statusSuccess(stadium, 'Stadium created successfully', 201);\n  });\n\n  update = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n    const stadium = await this.stadiumService.updateStadium(req.params.id as string, req.body);\n    if (!stadium) {\n      return (res as any).statusError('Stadium not found', 404);\n    }\n    (res as any).statusSuccess(stadium, 'Stadium updated successfully');\n  });\n\n  delete = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n    const stadium = await this.stadiumService.deleteStadium(req.params.id as string);\n    if (!stadium) {\n      return (res as any).statusError('Stadium not found', 404);\n    }\n    (res as any).statusSuccess(null, 'Stadium deleted successfully');\n  });\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776742381138}}
{"type":"message","id":"f8671e41","parentId":"39b71cb3","timestamp":"2026-04-21T03:33:23.462Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clearer picture. Let me wait for the prompt-optimizer agent to come back with the plan. While waiting, let me summarize what I've found so far.\n\nCurrent Status of Data Isolation:\n1. ✅ Dashboard - Teacher filtering OK\n2. ✅ Student - Teacher filtering OK\n3. ✅ Lesson - Teacher filtering OK\n4. ✅ Exam - Teacher filtering OK\n5. ❌ Course - NO teacher filtering (CRITICAL)\n6. ❌ Payment - NO teacher filtering (CRITICAL)\n7. ❓ Exam Batch - NO teacher filtering (needs check)\n8. ❓ Stadium - Likely admin-only (not teacher-specific)\n\nThe key issue is that Courses and Payments don't have teacher filtering. For Payments, the teacher relationship is via CourseStudent. For Courses, we need to determine how teachers relate to courses.","thinkingSignature":"328a83c198254aedf109c105089a12cd5f96e799264818d4eb809ba4a074c5b0"},{"type":"text","text":"Mình đợi prompt-optimizer agent hoàn thành. Trong lúc đó, đây là tổng hợp ban đầu:\n\n---\n\n## 📊 Phân Tích Hiện Trạng Phân Quyền\n\n### ✅ ĐÃ CÓ (Teacher Filtering):\n| Module | Status | Cách hoạt động |\n|--------|--------|----------------|\n| Dashboard | ✅ OK | Filter qua `CourseStudent.teacher_id` |\n| Student | ✅ OK | Kiểm tra `isStudentAssignedToTeacher()` |\n| Lesson | ✅ OK | Filter qua `teacher_id` |\n| Exam | ✅ OK | Filter qua `teacher_id` |\n\n### ❌ CẦN LÀM:\n| Module | Status | Vấn đề |\n|--------|--------|---------|\n| **Course** | ❌ CHƯA | Thấy TẤT CẢ courses |\n| **Payment** | ❌ CHƯA | Thấy TẤT CẢ payments |\n| **Exam Batch** | ❌ CHƯA | Không có filter |\n| Stadium | ⚠️ Cần xác định | Có thể admin-only |\n\n### 🔗 Data Relationships:\n```\nTeacher → CourseStudent(teacher_id) → Student → Course\n                    ↓\n              Payment (cần filter qua CourseStudent)\n```\n\n---\n\nĐang chờ prompt-optimizer agent để có SPEC chi tiết. Mình sẽ confirm với bạn trong giây lát."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1411,"output":507,"cacheRead":82085,"cacheWrite":1127,"totalTokens":85130,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776742381150,"responseId":"063622ee94b82d8cb7f16193ffe7246a"}}
